- The 'latest measurements' refer to the most recent records in the measurements table, based on the timestamp; 
- 'Alert statuses' are categorized as 'triggered' or 'resolved', with 'triggered' indicating an active alert and 'resolved' indicating an inactive alert; 
- 'Dashboard types' can be system or application dashboards; 
- 'Widget types' can be charts or tables.

